1.1.1.1
log
@import stalonetray 0.7.5

The stalonetray is a STAnd-aLONE system TRAY (notification area).  It
has minimal build and run-time dependencies: the Xlib only. The XEMBED
support is planned. Stalonetray runs under virtually any window manager.
